Concept Explanation ‚Üí Hardcoded URLs vs dynamic discovery, Eureka as a phonebook.

Demo ‚Üí Setup Eureka Server ‚Üí Register Hotel & Booking services ‚Üí Show Eureka dashboard.

Recap ‚Üí Summarize and preview API Gateway.

