Intro ‚Üí Why clients shouldn‚Äôt call microservices directly.

Concept ‚Üí API Gateway as entry point.

Demo ‚Üí Zuul setup ‚Üí Spring Cloud Gateway setup ‚Üí Show routing.

Recap ‚Üí Key learnings + next steps (circuit breakers).

