Concept ‚Üí Circuit Breaker, Retry, and comparison

Demo ‚Üí Implement Resilience4j circuit breaker in Booking Service

Failure Test ‚Üí Stop Payment Service, observe fallback

Recap ‚Üí Lighter, modular, better observability

Teaser ‚Üí Spring Cloud Gateway filters next

