# üå©Ô∏è Spring Cloud Hotel Booking System ‚Äî From Zero to Production

> üé• Built step-by-step in the YouTube series:  
> **[Spring Cloud Hotel Booking System - Complete Course](https://youtube.com/yourlink)**  
>  
> A production-grade **microservices architecture** built with **Spring Boot**, **Spring Cloud**, and **Kubernetes**, featuring real-world services like hotel management, booking, payments, and notifications.

---

## üèóÔ∏è System Overview

### Microservices
| Service | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| **Hotel Service** | Manages hotels & room availability |
| **Booking Service** | Handles reservations & cancellations |
| **Payment Service** | Processes payments |
| **Notification Service** | Sends booking confirmations |
| **User Service** | Authentication & user profiles |

---

## ‚òÅÔ∏è Spring Cloud Components

- **Spring Cloud Config** ‚Üí Centralized configuration  
- **Eureka Server** ‚Üí Service discovery  
- **OpenFeign** ‚Üí Declarative REST clients  
- **Gateway** ‚Üí Routing, auth, and filtering  
- **Sleuth + Zipkin** ‚Üí Distributed tracing  
- **Spring Cloud LoadBalancer** ‚Üí Modern load balancing  

---

## üß© Infrastructure Stack

| Category | Tool |
|-----------|------|
| **Logging** | ELK Stack (Elasticsearch, Logstash, Kibana) |
| **Monitoring** | Prometheus + Grafana |
| **Orchestration** | Kubernetes |
| **CI/CD** | GitHub Actions + Docker Hub |
| **Database** | MySQL |

